ent, solve puzzles, discover useful items, investigate clues, and find your way through a total of seven rooms in three areas to -hopefully- escape the basement!\n\n- Solve over a dozen puzzles, which includes smaller ones like finding keys or codes up to large ones which involve complex interactions with daunting machinery.\n\n- Explore three distinct areas with seven rooms, a total of 130 square meters, and more than 200 items to interact with. The game is designed for room scale and features a teleporting system.\n\n- In case you get stuck, a built-in hint system provides you with clues. You\u2019ll also get in-game statistics about your performance, and there are achievements to unlock!\n\nWill you take on the challenge? Will you manage to escape the basement?", "short_description": "You find yourself locked in the cell of an unknown basement with nothing else than a bed and a toilet. Can you escape? Explore the environment, solve puzzles, investigate clues, and find your way through a total of 7 rooms to -hopefully- escape the basement of this VR escape room game."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.escapevr.net/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Five Mind Creations UG (haftungsbeschr\u00e4nkt)", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.escapevr.net/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "394813081514456"}, {"id": "377978390272490"}, {"id": "275629210202852"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "de", "ru", "zh_CN", "zh_TW", "zh_HK", "en_US", "en_AU", "en_CA", "en_ZA", "en_GB"], "supported_input_devices